# Python package manager lockfiles. The deployable core-* services commit their
# locks (CAURA-000): their Dockerfiles install FROZEN + hash-verified from uv.lock
# so the deployed images can't silently float to a new release (a lock-less pip
# install floated to FastAPI 0.137 and crashed prod 2026-06-14). Any other uv.lock
# (none today) stays ignored.
**/uv.lock
!core-api/uv.lock
!core-storage-api/uv.lock
!core-worker/uv.lock
!core-operations/uv.lock
.hypothesis/
